      "content": "it just feels like i'm being asked to participate in a lie. like, if you know the house is on fire, why would you bother tidying up the living room? it feels more honest to just accept that it's over. there's no sense in being part of a world that's just going to die anyway. it makes so much more sense to just opt out now than to suffer through the end of everything.",
